    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section id="features" class="py-4">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row py-5">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h3>About Us</h3>
                    <p>Welcome to the Student Portal, your one-stop hub for all academic and campus-related activities. This portal is designed to provide students with easy access to important resources such as class schedules, grades, course materials, announcements, and campus news. It also offers tools for managing assignments, communicating with professors, and staying connected with fellow students. Whether you're registering for classes, checking your academic progress, or looking for campus events, the Student Portal ensures you have everything you need in one convenient location to succeed in your academic journey. Stay organized, informed, and engaged with the features and services available through your Student Portal!.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h3>Contact Us</h3>
                    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, we’re here to help! Our dedicated support team is available to guide you through any issues you may encounter while using the Student Portal. Whether you're experiencing technical difficulties, have inquiries about your account, or need clarification on any services, please don’t hesitate to reach out. You can contact us via email at student@cumous.co.za or use the live chat feature available on this page. Additionally, for urgent matters, feel free to call our support hotline at [phone number]. We're committed to providing timely and efficient support to ensure your experience with the Student Portal is seamless and stress-free.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h3>Visit Us</h3>
                    <p>We’d love to welcome you in person! If you need assistance or would like to speak with someone directly, feel free to visit us at our campus office. Our team is available during regular business hours to help with any questions or issues related to the Student Portal or any other academic services. The office is located at [Building Name, Room Number], [Campus Address], and is easily accessible for all students. Whether you need help navigating the portal or just want to connect with our support team, we’re here to ensure you have a smooth and successful experience. We look forward to seeing you soon!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
